      <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 0.8rem; line-height: 1.3; color: var(--text-primary); flex: 1;">Honestly assessing what the outcomes revealed</p>
      <p style="margin: auto 0 0 0; font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--text-secondary); text-transform: uppercase;">Performance • Lessons • Misconceptions • Gap Analysis</p>
