  <div style="width: 100%; text-align: center; margin-top: var(--spacing-lg); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);">
    <br>
    <strong style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 0.95rem;">Figure 1 — Design loop showing how structured observation, team alignment, and honest reflection drive continuous improvement toward justified decisions.</strong>
  </div>
</div>`
